            <div class="col s1"></div>
            <div class="col s5">
                <h4>How to save and access important information:</h4>
                <p>There are two ways to save information. You can either “star” the information for yourself or you can “pin” the information if it applies to every team member in the channel.</p>

                <p>Using the “star” feature:<br>
                    Clicking on the “star” icon lets you save information for yourself. You can always un-star if you no longer need the information.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col s5"><img class="rightContent materialboxed" alt="Save Information" src="/img/slack4.png"></div>
            <div class="col s1"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

