            <div class="col s1"></div>
            <div class="col s10">
                <h4>Extra information</h4>
                <p>To <strong>BOLD</strong> information, place to asterisks before and after the word i.e. *BOLD*</p>
                <p>To ITALICIZE information, place to underscores before and after the word i.e. _ITALICIZE_</p>
                <p>To quote something, put three dashes before and after the word i.e. ```quote```</p>
                <p>To highlight something in red, put one dash before and after the word i.e. `highlight`</p>
                <p>To insert gifs, write /gifs and push enter -  a menu of different gifs to choose from will come up.</p>
                <p>To insert polls, write /polly and push enter - a menu of how to create a poll will come up.</p>
                <p>Add Emojis to other peoples comments in Slack by clicking on the smiling face with a plus sign</p>
                <p>To start a thread click on the speech bubble with the three lines</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col s1"></div>
        </div>
